acy of 90%, demonstrating that the three groups are able to discern\ndistinct wake structures within a range of energy harvesting kinematics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Aug 2021 20:10:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-06"}
