 with opposite signs of inverse decay\nlengths, where half of the eigenstates are exponentially localized at one chain\nand the remainder of the eigenstates on the other chain. Our results provide a\nnew twist and insights for non-Hermitian phenomena in coupled non-Hermitian\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Aug 2021 08:47:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-06"}
