 damping, phase damping and depolarizing\nnoise, and even it reaches zero for $\\eta = 1$ in Brown \\emph{et al.} and\nBorras \\emph{et al.} channels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Aug 2021 14:26:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-30"}
