 of inferring certain global properties\nfrom local information in complex networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Aug 2021 02:22:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 2 Apr 2023 12:42:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-04"}
