predicted test outcomes for students. The authors recommend that\neducators use this or similar predictive methods responsibly and transparently,\nas one of many tools used to support students.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Aug 2021 03:55:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Mar 2022 07:10:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 9 Aug 2022 16:08:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-10"}
